104
00:05:11.300 --> 00:05:11.310
Mm-hmm.

105
00:05:11.440 --> 00:05:13.960
So covering what I said just before.

106
00:05:16.100 --> 00:05:19.980
Previous appointments are for three or five years, and so there are

107
00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:23.900
